{"tid":1798560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗咬狗骨單野一定要大力推","createTime":"2019-12-26T09:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T10:00:07.000Z","uid":338458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff261787a17cdc730699d147b47d7ed6674c92f","tid":1798560,"uid":338458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">防暴拉便衣只有有個可能性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 便衣犯法<br />\n2. 濫捕(暴)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月班藍絲都唔信濫捕同便衣有搞事<br />\n呢單野就係最有力嘅證據</span><br />\n<br />\n另外希望有記者朋友可以喺記招問:<br />\n「有防暴警察㩒住便衣，究竟係便衣犯左法，定係警察濫捕？」<br />\n只可以比小江2揀1，唔要open-end.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">希望黎緊嘅文宣可以循呢個方向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要話比班藍絲聽你都會比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c57df7181356247532065a6b2c7dc7302090dd53","tid":1798560,"uid":338458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09ce94b0498fa31bb4434bb4109c62287156861a","tid":1798560,"uid":338458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T09:57:36.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁，唔希有人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09180d79d2349740961db5c3b5006c09aef2d9e4","tid":1798560,"uid":201873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}